  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd8\u0daf \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0daf\u0dc3 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0da9\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "All ten of conscience to Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The group of 10 members of Hridiya Sakshie, who left the Podujana Peramuna and became independent, has also decided to support Podujana United Peramuna Member of Parliament Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma in tomorrow's election to appoint a new president.",
        "Anuradhapura District Member of Parliament K.P.S. Kumarasiri, Kandy District Members of Parliament Advocate Udayana Kirindigoda, Advocate Wasantha Yapa Bandara, Kurunegala District Member of Parliament Senior Lecturer Gunapala Ratnesekera, Kegalle District Members of Parliament Udayakantha Gunathilake, Sudath Manjula, Kalutara District Member of Parliament Lalit Ellawala, Ratnapura District Member of Parliament Ellina Akilasanavala and other signatures. It has been confirmed in a submitted letter."
      ],
